ZH: 我听到了一个响声。
EN: I heard a noise.
ZH: 那个门关上的响声很吵。
EN: The noise of the door closing was loud.
ZH: 我们走进房间时，听到了脚步声和响声。
EN: We heard footsteps and noises as we entered the room.
ZH: 森林里有很多奇怪的响声。
EN: There are many strange noises in the forest.
ZH: 外面的雷声震耳欲聋。
EN: The thunder outside was deafening.
ZH: 风声吹过窗户。
EN: The sound of the wind blowing through the window.
ZH: 我听到了水坑里的水声。
EN: I heard the sound of water in the puddle.
ZH: 车辆的轰鸣声越来越近。
EN: The roar of the vehicles was getting closer.
ZH: 鸟儿的鸣叫声在清晨响起。
EN: The chirping of the birds started in the early morning.
ZH: 街上传来了车辆的喇叭声。
EN: The honking of the vehicles could be heard from the street.
ZH: 敲门声打破了宁静。
EN: The knocking on the door broke the silence.
ZH: 他的脚步声在楼梯上回响。
EN: His footsteps echoed on the stairs.
ZH: 火车开过时，铁轨上发出了哗哗声。
EN: When the train passed by, there was a clattering sound on the tracks.
ZH: 沉闷的爆炸声在远处响起。
EN: The muffled sound of an explosion was heard in the distance.
ZH: 他的呼吸声在黑暗中回响。
EN: His breathing echoed in the darkness.
ZH: 桌子被拖动时发出了刺耳的摩擦声。
EN: The table made a grating noise as it was dragged.
ZH: 在山洞里传来远处的回音。
EN: Echoes came from afar in the cave.
ZH: 这杯子碎了，发出清脆的响声。
EN: The glass shattered, making a crisp sound.
ZH: 棒球击中木棍时发出了巨大的砰声。
EN: The baseball hitting the bat made a huge bang sound.
ZH: 警报器的声音很刺耳。
EN: The sound of the alarm was piercing.
